data.description: Seller offering a 2/1 Buydown with Preferred Lender . Welcome to 221 Lambert St, a stunning property located in the charming city of Leander, Texas, in the beautiful Larkspur development. This  home offers a generous living space of 2,523 square feet, providing ample room for comfortable living. With its desirable features and convenient layout, this property is sure to impress. The main level boasts a primary bedroom, offering convenience and privacy. This well-appointed bedroom provides a peaceful retreat with its spacious layout and en-suite bathroom. The en-suite bathroom features modern fixtures, a large shower, double vanity and a walk in closet. The kitchen also located on the main floor has beautiful shaker style cabinets and a large kitchen island with granite counter tops. The home also offers two additional bedrooms, perfect for accommodating family members or guests. .One of the highlights of this property is the two living spaces it offers. The main living area is located on the ground floor and provides an open concept layout, seamlessly connecting the kitchen, and dining area. This space is ideal for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones. The second living space is located on the upper level and can be used as a media room, home office, or playroom. For those who enjoy outdoor living, this home has both a balcony and an extended covered patio. The balcony provides a tranquil space to relax, while the covered patio offers shade and protection from the elements. These outdoor spaces are perfect for hosting gatherings or simply unwinding after a long day. Property has also been updated with a Rain Soft® EC5 water Conditioning system which  provides softened water throughout ($6,000+ new) This property benefits from its proximity to various amenities and attractions including Larkspur Elementary just a block away. Residents can take advantage of nearby parks, shopping centers, restaurants, and entertainment options.
